{"tid":1605022,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家真係唔好再幫襯m記","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T03:37:51.000Z","uid":9,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"37ca463c3430f8f22658433f33ed94be23f03f38","tid":1605022,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:01:07.000Z","msg":"已經唔係中唔中資嘅問題<br />\n班高層毫無良心可言<br />\n尋日金鐘海富大家都知發生咩事啦<br />\n出面掟哂催淚彈,水炮車都出動埋<br />\n成棟海富中心都因安全理由唔開<br />\nm記照樣做你生意,唔理員工安全<br />\n佢d高層有落到去睇㗎<br />\n覺得無問題咪繼續開鋪囉<br />\n之前有試過抽鮮風抽哂d催淚煙入去<br />\n係有員工感到不適<br />\n但佢地一於少理,繼續開鋪<br />\n(新聞都有出過係店舖附近掟催淚彈)<br />\n(個塊自動門玻璃隔得幾多?)<br />\n仲要之後拎佢地流哂眼水嘅相大造文章<br />\n衰撚過食人血饅頭<br />\n之後班高層話呢幾個月大家都辛苦<br />\n就有d卡送返比d員工<br />\n仆街,有d仲要比錢買嘅<br />\n黑心公司連自己員工都唔放過<br />\n<br />\n利申:員工,因為發夢而去返part time"},{"pid":"80e7bfa5a960de8a408eeb75cf71a63a78e62cd6","tid":1605022,"uid":235801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"俾我用埋啲卷都得呱，學生哥冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1723a0200eb5f3ec06bb662bf4f454457b42a88d","tid":1605022,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kUN6FB7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUN6FB7.jpg&h=77bb67cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XbuXNg7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbuXNg7.jpg&h=66ae45f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f9fd4bcc5ed1f7b806deda5d57fcf68ada78b70","tid":1605022,"uid":263667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學界外國戰線一路努力緊同外國政府進行遊說工作<br />\n希望大家能夠支持眾籌，目標只係300萬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif